extend layout
block content
  p This is a demo application to import OPML (outline) files into 
    a(href="http://coggle.it") Coggle.
  
  if !(access_tokens && access_tokens.coggle)
    p To get started, grant access to your Coggle account:
    p
      a(href="/auth/coggle") Authorize access to Coggle

  else
    div#drop-target
      p drag and drop files here

      div#files

  if access_tokens
    p.logout
      a(href="/auth/deauth") Logout.
